<p></p><hr><p></p>
<p></p><h1>WEEK 6 =E2=80=94 Sound + Multisensory</h1><p></p>
<p><br></p>
<p></p><h2>Objectives</h2><p></p>
<p></p><ul><li>
<p>Add auditory layer (often neglected but critical)</p>
