# Instructor Guide

## What to Buy
Recommended initial purchase set:
- 8 to 10 Meta Quest headsets
- 1 month of Meshy subscriptions for the course if budget allows
- optional over-ear or on-ear audio solutions if sound design matters
- optional external battery packs for longer sessions

Do not spend early money on:
- expensive DCC suites
